message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's worth more than $12000 to me, but considering its value to you, I'm willing to start the negotiation at $9500. Let me know if this works for you or if you'd like to propose a counteroffer.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $10000 for the product.
